sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as caller
    participant E as ECCDataLayer
    participant B as backing layer (RawNAND)
    participant D as ECCDecoder

    C->>E: read(offset, length)
    Note over E: compute page range<br/>from NANDGeometry

    loop for each NAND page in range
        E->>B: read(page_addr, page_size + oob_size)
        B-->>E: raw page + spare (OOB)
        Note over E: split page_data | ecc_bytes<br/>from spare area
        E->>D: decode(page_data, ecc_bytes)
        alt decode succeeds
            D-->>E: corrected bytes
        else uncorrectable
            D-->>E: raise / flag bad page
            Note over E: mark region, continue
        end
    end

    E-->>C: concatenated corrected bytes
